ng#Signs\" title=\"Crafting\">Signs</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dark_Sign\" title=\"Dark Sign\">Dark Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Stone_Sign\" title=\"Stone Sign\">Stone Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Text_Sign\" title=\"Text Sign\">Text Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Wood_Sign\" title=\"Wood Sign\">Wood Sign</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Misc\" title=\"Crafting\">Misc</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Anvil\" title=\"Anvil\">Anvil</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee_Maker\" title=\"Coffee Maker\">Coffee Maker</a> • <a href=\"/Cookout_Kit\" title=\"Cookout Kit\">Cookout Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Deconstructor\" title=\"Deconstructor\">Deconstructor</a> • <a href=\"/Fairy_Dust\" title=\"Fairy Dust\">Fairy Dust</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Computer\" title=\"Farm Computer\">Farm Computer</a> • <a href=\"/Hopper\" title=\"Hopper\">Hopper</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Forge\" title=\"Mini-Forge\">Mini-Forge</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Jukebox\" title=\"Mini-Jukebox\">Mini-Jukebox</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Shipping_Bin\" title=\"Mini-Shipping Bin\">Mini-Shipping Bin</a> • <a href=\"/Sewing_Machine\" title=\"Sewing Machine\">Sewing Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Staircase\" title=\"Staircase\">Staircase</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_Blessings\" title=\"Statue Of Blessings\">Statue Of Blessings</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_The_Dwarf_King\" title=\"Statue Of The Dwarf King\">Statue Of The Dwarf King</a> •  <a href=\"/Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\">Telephone</a> • <a href=\"/Tent_Kit\" title=\"Tent Kit\">Tent Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">Tools</a> • <a href=\"/Workbench\" title=\"Workbench\">Workbench</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414062438\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.136 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.153 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2352/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 15576/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1476/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2192/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 517 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   72.982      1 -total\n 61.82%   45.114      1 Template:Infobox_cooking\n 28.84%   21.050      1 Template:Description\n 25.00%   18.245      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 20.86%   15.225      3 Template:Name\n  4.82%    3.515      1 Template:History\n  4.51%    3.291      3 Template:Price\n  2.84%    2.075      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  2.51%    1.831      1 Template:Version\n  1.79%    1.306      1 Template:NavboxEquipment\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:11984-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414062438 and revision id 190377\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "<onlyinclude>{{{{{1|Infobox cooking}}}\n|name        = Hyper Speed-Gro\n|image       = Hyper Speed-Gro.png\n|description = {{Description|Hyper Speed-Gro}}\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|sellprice   = 70\n|recipe      = [[Qi's Walnut Room]] for {{Price|30|gem}}\n|ingredients = {{Name|Radioactive Ore|1}}{{Name|Bone Fragment|3}}{{Name|Solar Essence|1}}\n|qiseasoning = false\n}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Hyper Speed-Gro''' is a [[Fertilizer]] that speeds crop growth by 33% (or a total of 43% with the [[Skills#Farming|Agriculturist Profession]])<ref name=\"speedincrease\" />. It can be [[Crafting|crafted]] after purchasing the recipe from [[Qi's Walnut Room]] for {{Price|30|gem}}.\n\nHyper Speed-Gro can be placed on tilled soil ''before or after'' planting a seed, or at any stage of crop growth. It does not reduce time between harvests for multi-harvest crops.\n\nApplying Hyper Speed-Gro days after planting a seed still decreases the time it takes to fully grow, but it reduces a fixed amount of days per stage for each crop regardless of the day it's applied, and the reduction in stages that the crop has already passed will not retroactively apply. Combined with the fact that the reduction disproportionately affects earlier stages more, this means that its reduction to the rest of the growth time is much lower than the advertised percentage of 33%.<ref name=\"speedincrease2\" />\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|dislike=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nHyper Speed-Gro is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nHyper Speed-Gro can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[File:Shirt174.png|24px|link=]] [[Tailoring#Shirts|High-Waisted Shirt]]. It is not used in [[dyeing]].\n\n==Quests==\nHyper Speed-Gro is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"speedincrease\">See <samp>StardewValley.TerrainFeatures.HoeDirt::applySpeedIncreases</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n<ref name=\"speedincrease2\">The change in phaseDays in <samp>HoeDirt::applySpeedIncreases</samp> is static regardless of the date of fertilizer application relative to the date of planting. This means that applying fertilizer after planting only affects the current stage and any stages thereafter, in the same way that applying at the same day as planting affects those stages.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Introduced.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Fertilizer]]\n\n[[de:Hyper Speed-Zücht]]\n[[es:Fertilizante ultra-rápido]]\n[[fr:Vitesse grand V]]\n[[it:Iper-Crescipresto]]\n[[ja:グングンノビールハイパー]]\n[[ko:하이퍼 성장 촉진제]]\n[[hu:Hiper gyorsnövesztő]]\n[[pt:Hiper Solo Foliar]]\n[[ru:Гипер СкороРост]]\n[[tr:Aşırı Hızlı-Ek]]\n[[zh:顶级生长激素]]"
    }
